metadata.symbol: Audiovisual digital art by Massimo Magee
metadata.Description: Shunt Proof is an audiovisual digital art object by Massimo Magee, designed to be read by the computer as both a visual still image and as a piece of audio, these being two readings of the same file. It was created with processed image data, virtual drums and virtual guitar generated from the image data, and live tenor saxophone. NFT includes lossless and lossy versions of both visual and audio readings - 2777x2777px, 5min50sec.
